headline: Auto Parts Retailer Stocks Q1 Earnings: Advance Auto Parts (NYSE:AAP) Firing on All Cylinders
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at auto parts retailer stocks, starting with Advance Auto Parts (NYSE:AAP).
